{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id781639d9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470ll"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"470ll"},"text":"§ 470ll.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual report to Congress","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"As part of the annual report required to be submitted to the specified committees of the Congress pursuant to section 469a–3(c) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002396"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002396"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title, the Secretary of the Interior shall comprehensively report as a separate component on the activities carried out under the provisions of this chapter, and he shall make such recommendations as he deems appropriate as to changes or improvements needed in the provisions of this chapter. Such report shall include a brief summary of the actions undertaken by the Secretary under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s470jj"},"text":"section 470jj of this title","children":[],"tail":", relating to cooperation with private individuals."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id781639da-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/95/s13"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–95, § 13","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-10-31"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1979","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/93/728"},"text":"93 Stat. 728","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id781639db-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id781639dc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id781639dd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s469a–3"},"text":"Section 469a–3 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, was repealed and restated as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s312504"},"text":"section 312504 of Title 54","children":[],"tail":", National Park Service and Related Programs, by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287","children":[],"tail":", §§ 3, 7, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3094"},"text":"128 Stat. 3094","children":[],"tail":", 3272. Prior to repeal of section 469a–3, language in subsec. (c) of that section that required submission of an annual report was struck out by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/333"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–333","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
